    "headline": "Flowco Holdings Inc. Announces Appointment of New Independent Director",
    "summary": "HOUSTON, May 01, 2026--Flowco Holdings Inc. (NYSE: FLOC) (\"Flowco\" or the \"Company\") announced that its Board of Directors (the \"Board\") has appointed Hardy Murchison as an independent director, effective April 29, 2026. The appointment increases the size of the Board to eight directors and the number of independent directors from three to four.",
